[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "……では。\n対カウントダウンフェス審査作戦会議を始めまする！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00465",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "わーい！　どんどん！　ぱふぱふ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00466",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "焦点は、どうやって「人気」になるかよね。\nそんな簡単になれたら、今までも苦労してないんだけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00467",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "ライブの動員実績は今からではどうにもならないで\nござろう。であれば、取れる道はそれ以外",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00468",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ＳＮＳのフォロワー数とか、勢いをなんとかするって\nことだよね？　なにすればいいんだろう？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00469",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "私たちはアイドルなのよ。ダンスとか歌の動画を\nアップするに決まってるじゃない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00470",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "それだけで人気が出るのかなあ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00471",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "拙者たちレベルの駆け出しグループとなると、\nなんらかのバズは狙わないと厳しいでしょうなあ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00472",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "圧倒的技術力を見せつければいいってことじゃない。\nなに？　自信ないの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00473",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "んー……そうじゃなくて。\nもっと違うことをしたほうがいいんじゃないかな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00474",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "「なになにしてみた！」とか、「右左どっち！」とか、\nそういうの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00475",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "……それ、アイドルがすること？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00476",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "今アタシたちがやらなくちゃいけないのは、\n人気になることだよ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00477",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "アイドルがどうとか、関係ないと思うんだ。\nなんでもやらなくちゃ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00478",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "それは……そうかもしれないわね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00479",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "……イザナの言う通り。アイドルという枠に\nとらわれすぎていたやもしれませぬ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00480",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "とはいえ、ブランディングというものがありまする。\n内容については社長殿の確認を取るようにいたそう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00481",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "じゃあ、早速動画を撮るわよ！\n使うのはスマホでいいの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00482",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "いいんじゃないかな？　編集のやり方とかは、\n分からないけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00483",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "……拙者か！？　もちろん、分からないでござる！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00484",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "まあ、そうよね。疎そうだし。機械とか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00485",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "もしかして口調からそう言っているでござるか！？\nそれは偏見でありまする！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00486",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "どうしよっか……アイデアは考えるとして、\nそういった技術的なことを相談できる人がいたらなあ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00487",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "うーん……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00488",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "イザナちゃーん、いるー？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00489",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "レスナちゃん！　どうしてここに？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00490",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "今日も部室で調合の練習してたんだ。\nお昼の時間になったから、一緒に食べないかなって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00491",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "もうそんな時間でござるか。\n拙者たちも一息つくといたしましょう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00492",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "なんだか皆さん、難しそうな顔をしてましたね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00493",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "実は、次のライブに向けてやらなきゃいけない\nことがあって……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00494",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "なるほど……バズる動画を作りたくて、\n技術的なサポートをしてくれる人が欲しい……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00495",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "私、心当たりがあります！　相談してみますので、\n少しお待ちいただいてもいいでしょうか！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00496",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "本当！？　さすがレスナちゃん！\n頼りになるー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00497",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "この前の錬金術の演出といい、あんたすごいわね……\nどんな人生送ったら、そんな豊かな経験が積めるわけ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00498",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "ここ半年で、色々ありまして……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00499",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "とにもかくにも、ありがたいでござる！　技術者の\nツテについてはレスナ殿にお任せいたしましょう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00500",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "拙者たちは、内容のほうを練るということで。\nでは、いったんお昼休憩でござる！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00501",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]